{"tid":2329511,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"PTU執信用卡狂碌 賴社運爆發遭孤立  貪兩部iPhone「被捕後頓感解脫」","createTime":"2020-12-17T09:29:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-17T10:31:43.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"65578878a5800862ff765fa9685d8916655df342","tid":2329511,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T09:29:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201217/XKORTIN72ZEIZPDRZZYRUIHZX4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201217%2FXKORTIN72ZEIZPDRZZYRUIHZX4%2F&d=%2B0Qob83dP4InFIGdpve28aooFDKVeMyzaQj0gYzwHSI%3D&h=a0c9e310\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201217%2FXKORTIN72ZEIZPDRZZYRUIHZX4%2F&h=930a03e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201217/XKORTIN72ZEIZPDRZZYRUIHZX4/</a><br />\n<br />\nPTU執信用卡狂碌 賴社運爆發遭孤立 <br />\n貪兩部iPhone「被捕後頓感解脫」<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】機動部隊警員聲稱因去年社會運動而遭親友孤立，情緒打擊下終日自閉在家；一次休班時，他在戲院取去別人遺下的信用卡，然後瘋狂碌卡購物，包括在Apple Store 購買兩部手提電話，涉款約2.5萬元。警員昨承認盜竊罪及以欺騙手段取得財產罪，在求情信中強調在警隊從未做過錯事。裁判官張志偉認為被告所為不是最嚴重的罪行，決定先為被告索取社會服務令報告，兼批准警員保釋，押後至本月30日判刑。<br />\n<br />\n現已被停職的被告李卓軒（28歲）昨出庭應訊，親友坐滿法庭。辯方大狀呈上被告過往證書及求情信件，指被告自2011年中七畢業後，曾任職不同工作，三年前加入警隊，短時間內減去60磅，通過體能測試完成課程。<br />\n<br />\n大律師續指，自去年社會運動後，被告因警員身份而遭親友疏遠，感到鬱悶，終日自閉在家，友人更向他借貸五萬元不還。被告獨自往戲院看戲，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n惟根據案情，被告於警誡下承認貪心犯案，指涉案手機已在案發當天即日以兩萬元出售。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/UWrI2jwyH8tnx1pkv9IfRNidx1U=/3652x2054/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/CEFMZX7KXZGXDKFPRKCIXK2HFQ.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FUWrI2jwyH8tnx1pkv9IfRNidx1U%3D%2F3652x2054%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FCEFMZX7KXZGXDKFPRKCIXK2HFQ.JPG&h=cc4159f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■被告警員李卓軒昨出庭應訊求情，獲准保釋候懲。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n官不排除判監<br />\n<br />\n裁判官指，被告因一時貪念犯案，無刑事紀錄，其後願意作出賠償，都是有力的求情因素。法庭認為被告所為不是最嚴重的罪行，故先索取社會服務令報告，但稱不表示不會判監。<br />\n<br />\n被告承認於去年10月14日在太古城中心5樓MOViE MOViE Cityplaza，偷竊黃姓事主的信用卡，並於同日冒認卡主用該信用卡，到銅鑼灣希慎廣場Apple Store購買24,998元產品。他另被控取得MOViE MOViE Cityplaza的33元財物，則獲控方撤控。被告早前一度要求押後案件，讓他致函律政司商討處理案件方法。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：ESCC2438/20<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/0-EuyG6b9beulR-UTutENZUwY84=/1328x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/Q3XBOCBFUJBDTLVYYLYP5H4ZRQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F0-EuyG6b9beulR-UTutENZUwY84%3D%2F1328x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FQ3XBOCBFUJBDTLVYYLYP5H4ZRQ.jpg&h=6825e4a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■被告去年在太古城MOViE MOViE戲院取走事主信用卡。資料圖片"},{"pid":"0569ce839574ec1cc9b7c42bb24ce82dbd3ece8e","tid":2329511,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T09:30:23.000Z","msg":"被捕師<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ac9e0394cdf3ea593852bc85626759ddde422e4","tid":2329511,"uid":261172,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T09:31:25.000Z","msg":"解脫是不夠的<br />\n<br />\n坐監令人生更精彩的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fefb84528b9b37079aceeb5e90637b082932b5fb","tid":2329511,"uid":39710,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T09:32:59.000Z","msg":"2小時社會服務令算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c88997d9f0fdf12afef20205dbc0d6ca86323fd3","tid":2329511,"uid":133824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-17T09:33:15.000Z","msg":"入去坐下咪無咁孤獨囉"},{"pid":"d4a6d43936